Dependencies
============

aptitude install python-pexpect

What is ashttp ?
================

ashttp can serve any text application over http, like :

$ ashttp 8080 top
to serve a top on port 8080, or :

$ ashttp 8080 watch -n 1 ls -lah /tmp
to serve an actualized directory listing of /tmp

LICENSE
=======

ashttp use a modified version of the vt100 emulator found in pexpect,
you'll find the pexpect licence in the file python-pexpect-licence

The ashttp licence is under FreeBSD Licence that you can found in the copyright
file
